e01664fa6d4c6a75210cd35b4f263f05138b8"},"reactions":[{"id":"2810750","commentID":2849568,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0xe9519b54f203dc3b39c3a07137d47728fb4981fe","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x0e3ed3bb34f90a1a72d19e5a7b13b624cf488694"}},{"id":"2810737","commentID":2849568,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0x6aba547b01f9305a6e89390dba7090f4f3f34886","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0xe5052db3c454e1235fd19cd662e129234e26600c"}},{"id":"2810903","commentID":2849568,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0x1901a32d6264e24d8291166b887dd4af6507ade7","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x918f4872e2675144bbe8c1db33069db57ff566ad"}},{"id":"2810998","commentID":2849568,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0xc33348a77b4e948c4cad6562aacf59e895c4d073","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x6790c522a3fcdaa1b5f4d7cc6cdb21689e63c9e9"}}],"reportCount":0,"reactionCount":4},{"id":"2849569","body":"2. Procedural Estoppel: The market precedent was set on April 7. The ceasefire was facilitated and confirmed via the Pakistani mediator. If the DVM accepted the mediator's agency for the first half of this event, it is intellectually dishonest to reject the exact same agency for the extension. One cannot change the verification standard mid-game to suit a 99.8% position.","parentEntityType":"Event","parentEntityID":357625,"parentCommentID":"2849568","userAddress":"0xa1ce01664fa6d4c6a75210cd35b4f263f05138b8","replyAddress":"0xa1ce01664fa6d4c6a75210cd35b4f263f05138b8","createdAt":"2026-04-27T12:49:39.680542Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-27T12:49:53.300014Z","profile":{"name":"0x920ab2760C5B4BE099328665E45Bb833d30D32C9-1773892601412","pseudonym":"Boring-Comportment","displayUsernamePublic":true,"proxyWallet":"0x920ab2760c5b4be099328665e45bb833d30d32c9","baseAddress":"0xa1ce01664fa6d4c6a75210cd35b4f263f05138b8"},"reactions":[{"id":"2810751","commentID":2849569,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0xe9519b54f203dc3b39c3a07137d47728fb4981fe","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x0e3ed3bb34f90a1a72d19e5a7b13b624cf488694"}},{"id":"2810905","commentID":2849569,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0x1901a32d6264e24d8291166b887dd4af6507ade7","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x918f4872e2675144bbe8c1db33069db57ff566ad"}},{"id":"2811004","commentID":2849569,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0xc33348a77b4e948c4cad6562aacf59e895c4d073","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x6790c522a3fcdaa1b5f4d7cc6cdb21689e63c9e9"}}],"reportCount":0,"reactionCount":3},{"id":"2849607","body":"3. De Facto Reality Over De Jure Semantics: Ceasefires in volatile regions are often \"functional\" before they are \"formal.\" Global Tier 1 media confirmed the extension was active. The oracle’s job is to reflect the truth of the event, not to be a gatekeeper for Iranian bureaucracy.\n\nTo vote NO is to vote for the destruction of the contract’s original text in favor of whale-driven narrative manipulation. We must uphold the \"OR\" clause.","parentEntityType":"Event","parentEntityID":357625,"parentCommentID":"2849568","userAddress":"0xa1ce01664fa6d4c6a75210cd35b4f263f05138b8","replyAddress":"0xa1ce01664fa6d4c6a75210cd35b4f263f05138b8","createdAt":"2026-04-27T13:01:30.695814Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-27T13:01:44.909717Z","profile":{"name":"0x920ab2760C5B4BE099328665E45Bb833d30D32C9-1773892601412","pseudonym":"Boring-Comportment","displayUsernamePublic":true,"proxyWallet":"0x920ab2760c5b4be099328665e45bb833d30d32c9","baseAddress":"0xa1ce01664fa6d4c6a75210cd35b4f263f05138b8"},"reactions":[{"id":"2810906","commentID":2849607,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0x1901a32d6264e24d8291166b887dd4af6507ade7","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x918f4872e2675144bbe8c1db33069db57ff566ad"}}],"reportCount":0,"reactionCount":1},{"id":"2849329","body":"Look at the order book. The \"NO\" whales are buying in at 99.8%. They aren’t just betting; they are trying to bulldoze us. They think this is a \"sure thing.\" They think we are weak, that we don’t understand the rules, and that they can simply \"eat\" our positions through sheer capital arrogance.\n\nThey are wrong